    Text Splitter categories (langchain-text-splitters):
      Text-structure (recommended default):
        RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter
          -> use from_language() for source code
             (Python, JS, TS, Markdown, HTML, Go ...)
      Length-based:
        CharacterTextSplitter  (single separator)
        TokenTextSplitter      (tiktoken)
        SentenceTransformersTokenTextSplitter
      Document-structure (standalone, not TextSplitter):
        MarkdownHeaderTextSplitter  (# / ## / ### headers)
        HTMLHeaderTextSplitter      (h1..h4 tags)
        RecursiveJsonSplitter       (JSON objects/arrays)
      Sentence-level NLP:
        SpacyTextSplitter  (spaCy pipeline)
        NLTKTextSplitter   (NLTK punkt)
    MarkdownHeaderTextSplitter, HTMLHeaderTextSplitter,
    and RecursiveJsonSplitter are standalone classes and
    do NOT extend TextSplitter.
  end note
