  note as JumpNote
    Agent jump system - short-circuit the loop:
    Any node-style hook can return "jump_to" to
    redirect execution:
      return {
        "messages": [...],
        "jump_to": "end"
      }
    Valid targets:
      "end"   -> skip to after_agent (or END node)
      "tools" -> jump to tools node
